'''Félicité Niyitegeka''' (yavutse mu 1934) Ni Umubikira w'[[Rwanda|umunyarwandakazi]] ubarwa mu ntwari z'igihugu, yavukiye  i Vumbi, mu cyahoze ari komini ya Runyinya, muri perefegitura ya [[Butare]]<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/felicite-niyitegeka-was-always-heroine</ref><ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/abazi-niyitegeka-felicite-bahamya-ko-ubutwari-bwe-ari-ubwa-kera</ref>

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
. Ni bucura y'umuryango w'abana 10, Félicité yize mumashuri abanza ya Astrida, hanyuma yiga ayisumbuye mu ishuri rya Save mumashuri acungwa n'ababikira<ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/politiki/article/ibaruwa-iteye-agahinda-intwari-felicite-yandikiye-musaza-we-col-nzungize</ref>. Arangije amasomo ye mu myaka ya za 1950, Félicité yahawe inshingano yo kuba umwarimu n'umugenzuzi mu majyaruguru y'u [[Rwanda]], mu ishuri rya Muramba<ref>https://thebridge.rw/niyitegeka-felicite-intwari-yigihugu-mu-rwego-rwimena/</ref>. Icyo gihe yahawe na “Auxiliaires de l'Apostolat”, yitwa “Demoiselles”. Paruwasi ya Nyundo na seminari ya Nyundo yari imaze gushingwa ihabwa umwepiskopi w[[Rwanda|'umunyarwanda]], [[Aloys Bigirumwami|Nyiricyubahiro Aloys Bigirumwami.]]<ref>https://real-life-heroes.fandom.com/wiki/F%C3%A9licit%C3%A9_Niyitegeka</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/189549</ref><ref name=":0">https://www.ascleiden.nl/content/webdossiers/ascl-rwanda-collection</ref>
Félicité yavukiye mu muryango ufite kwizera Gukomeye muri Kristo, ise Simon Sekabwa yari umukiristu bikomeye.<ref>https://fortuneofafrica.com/rwanda/felicite-niyitegeka/</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201402030649.html</ref>  Félicité yabaye umugore wa mbere [[Afurika|w’umunyafurika]] wabaye Auxiliaires de l'Apostolat2<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/abazi-niyitegeka-felicite-bahamya-ko-ubutwari-bwe-ari-ubwa-kera</ref>. Auxiliaires de l'Apostolat intego yabo ni ugukorana bya hafi na musenyeri, Auxiliaires de l'Apostolat bitwaga [[Ikinyarwanda|Kinyarwanda]] "Abakobwa ba Musenyeri", [[Aloys Bigirumwami|Nyiricyubahiro Bigirumwami]] yohereje Félicité i Lourdes kugira ngo ahugurwe, aho ikigo cy’amahugurwa ku Isi cy’abafasha ba Apostolate giherereye<ref>https://cnlg.gov.rw/fileadmin/templates/documents/ENGLISH_final.pdf</ref>.<ref>https://www.sapiens.org/culture/rwandan-genocide-rescuers/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Tugarutse mu [[Rwanda]], Félicité yabaye umwe mu bayobozi ba Auxiliaires de l'Apostolat<ref name=":0" />. Umuyobozi wa mbere w’ishuri rikuru “Notre-Dame d'Afrique” rya Nyundo<ref>https://dbpedia.org/page/F%C3%A9licit%C3%A9_Niyitegeka</ref>, umwepiskopi yamwohereje i Lourdes mu 1963, kugira ngo ajyane nabandi bagenzi be bo muri [[Afurika]] bahugurirwe hamwe<ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2017/01/the-catholic-nun-who-rejected-armed-escorts/</ref>. Yagarutse nyuma y'imyaka itandatu ashingwa kuyobora ubuyobozi bwa Centre Saint Pierre, ikigo cya diyosezi cyari ishinzwe amahugurwa n’umwiherero wa Auxiliaires de l'Apostolat<ref>https://www.atlasobscura.com/articles/felicite-niyitegeka-genocide-rwanda</ref>. Icyubahiro cye cyambutse umupaka kugera i [[Goma]], muri [[Zayire]] [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|(Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]]), aho yakoranye na bagenzi be<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/104911/amagambo-yavuzwe-na-niyitegeka-felicite-uri-mu-ntwari-zigihugu-yakozwemo-indirimbo-video-104911.html</ref>. .Félicité yahoraga yifuza kwitangira umurimo , cyane cyane ku babikeneye cyane. Yabigaragaje muri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yakorewe abatutsi]] mu [[Rwanda]] mu 1994<ref>https://www.atlasobscura.com/articles/felicite-niyitegeka-genocide-rwanda</ref><ref>https://bangambiki.wordpress.com/2012/02/05/intwari-zu-rwanda-felicite-niyitegeka/</ref>.

Mu gukora urutonde rw'intwari z'igihugu, abayobozi basanze ubutwari bwe mubuzima bwe bwose bumwemerera kuba kurutonde maze yegurwa kuba intwari y'igihugu cy'u [[Rwanda]]. Ibi byatewe n'icyemezo cy'inama y'abaminisitiri yabaye ku ya 12 Nzeri 2011<ref>https://real-life-heroes.fandom.com/wiki/F%C3%A9licit%C3%A9_Niyitegeka</ref><ref>https://www.dwci.edu/download_file/view/1128/357</ref>.

